description:
Welcome to the Alpha 7 Trading Academy's Day Trading Market Structure Signals course. This course will teach you simple powerful setups using a simple 3-candle sequence. You'll learn to trade market structure highs and lows and equipping the rifle chart as well as a step-by-step process for identifying and executing the strategy in a do-it-yourself style.

This short course will teach you a simple & effective day-trading strategy and provide you with the tools you'll need to master the strategy. Watch as the strategy is put to the test during live market conditions for a $290 profit on one day. The best part is the course is free and the strategy is transparent, easy-to-use and most importantly, effective.
title: Day Trading Market Structure Signals
